Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once a businessman in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I now work for a shipping\Ncompany in the South China Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that one, we're done transferring\Nthe crates. Would you please sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could somebody please sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing special about it.\NWe're just a mediocre shipping company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times, we even brush up against\Nthe law to put food on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So everything's okay, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All okay, and I even got them to sign.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should also have cargo from them\Nfor us to take back. Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well yeah, I did get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, ask them to use the crane again\Nand get down here with the shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the troublemaker is being useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to say that,\Nbut nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that his white collar look\Nwas perfect for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he worried about the cargo\Nwe're taking back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's helpless. It's just some cheap job\Nfrom the Manisarera cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I counted the crates we delivered\Nlike you wanted me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I brought the shipment\Nwe're taking back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure he's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we arrive at Hat Yai, we hand\Nhim over to a buyer carrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...designated by the Colombian Mafioso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, put him in a cabin for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:04:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you fight back. This way.\NHey. Come on. Get in this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like he was gonna puke.\NHe's still not a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a shipping company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take shipments to their\Ndesignated destinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where our responsibilities end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get too attached to the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Rock.\N- Want to see what you had for breakfast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you trade\Nbabysitting duties with Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Her professionalism is a problem.\N- Get over here! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't deliver\Na shipment full of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Taking advantage of my kindness!\N- Hey, Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you looking at?!\N- That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need something\Nas good as a cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ought to chain him up and throw\Nhim in storage. That brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of the sea.\NHe can't escape. We don't need chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, it'll only be for a little\Nwhile, but we'll be traveling together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can at least stop throwing\Nfood at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That friendly talk will rot your mouth.\NSaint Maria can see through it, villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm aware that my words\Nmay not be appropriate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since I'm helping these guys out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're different from the tattooed\Nwoman or the big black man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must seem like it.\NI'm just a villain in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who put me on the boat\Ndidn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be sold off\Nsomewhere, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I know my father will save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? But aren't you an orphan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that? The cartel?\NThey're big liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is a member of one of\Nthe great thirteen families...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Diego Jose San Fernando Lovelace,\Nthe eleventh head of the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Garcia Lovelace, his only son\Nand the next head of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for pity,\Nyou won't find it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna lie you should\Ncome up with a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pity? Don't be stupid. What could\NI gain from lying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty unlikable kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear\Nthe name Lovelace, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the lowest noble house\Nof the thirteen families.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that makes it a little\Nmore believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, things haven't been going well\Nlately. But we've been getting by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is kind of old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never got involved\Nin unnecessary side businesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our business wasn't going well,\Nbut the plantations were stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Until the mafia came, that is.\N- And that's who kidnapped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a gift for making up stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came to buy our land by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A geological test showed that\Nlanthanides could be found there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my father refused,\Nthey showed their true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They began harassing our farms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But father still wouldn't nod his head.\NThat's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanthanides?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also called rare earth.\NDon't you know your periodic table?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Where did you learn\Na word like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't believe me.\NThat's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to make you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you know about\Nrare earth... lanthanides?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lutetium, atomic number 71,\Nwas found on our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's used as a fixing agent for\Nceramics. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lovelace household has a dog.\NAbout that dog. What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy. That dog became a member\Nof our family six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Lazlo, a Volpino Italiano\Nwith a white coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. Rock is taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably getting himself\Nemotionally worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably give us a sad story\Nand ask us to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?\NWith eyes just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. I don't like how this feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after we dock, I think we should\Nwait before handing him to the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cartel was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're lying, there must be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have pity for our cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you try to imagine where people\Nwho are sold will end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as there's a profit for\Nour company, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? There's no problem\Nfrom that point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will keep turning\Neven if there is no justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said I didn't pity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also concerned\Nthat our client lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be in the resource procurement\Ndepartment of my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a lot about rare earth\Nand rare metals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's correct in what he says\Nabout the Lovelace family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing reports from\Nour South American division.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family structure and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. That's impressive, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very brilliant businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get you some of Mama's\Nhomemade cherry pie as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it's up to Dutch.\NI'll go with what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it. The moment\Nthey had the kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they could've demanded a ransom\Nand accomplished their goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any reason for them to keep it\Na secret and sell him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why they'd\Nkeep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But selling him off has a simple and\Nclear logic. They were pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing mafias\Nand cartels hate worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than having shit rubbed\Nin their faces. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Revy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if their face is what's at stake\Nthen this is gonna be a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put a little insurance on\Nour shipment before we deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Balalaika to check\Nbehind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. It's rare to have you\Nasking a favor, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need details about the relationship{\i0}\N{\i1}between the Manisarera cartel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and the Lovelace family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you prepare that for us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We actually just received a job\Nconcerning Manisarera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your timing's great, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks. I owe you one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since we're still just\Nsetting up insurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can I ask that\Nyou don't stir things up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our business, if things get stirred,\Nthey get stirred up like a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just do your best, do it cool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Shall I get back\Nto you at your office?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. We'll be waiting at the Yellow Flag{\i0}\N{\i1}having a drink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, Rock. There's one more\Nthing we need to check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Lovelace father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really the type to use mercenaries\Nto rescue hostages, like the kid implied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Financially speaking, they can barely\Nafford to keep one servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A servant? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary house maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think the maid's gonna rush in to save\Nthe little prince? That would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a lonely soul who has come\Nall the way from South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in search of a place where I can\Nfind my fellow countrymen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By fellow countrymen, you mean\Nfrom your country?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This little lady's countrymen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could she mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are no other "countrymen"\Nof her's in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really can't tell you ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who may I ask that could tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss. There is a place where you\Nmight be able to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that place is like a den of gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not worry. So long as I can\Nfind out about my countrymen there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wouldn't recommend\Nthat place, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here. We're on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you get moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the disposition of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be a brat too, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then pay me for my work as a babysitter.\NThis isn't even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna treat him nice and get a job\Nat his house? Guess that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be better off as\Na white-faced butler than a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asking, "Master, would you like\Nsome Mint Julep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Old Black Joe, must be nice\Nto be surrounded by dozens of servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you before,\Nwe only have one servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maid named Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though she's a maid,\Nshe's no good at cleaning or chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't serve milk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then may I have a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only arrived here today and\NI do not know my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in search of a Colombian friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bar. Order a real drink.\NYou dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only arrived here today and\NI do not know my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in search of\Na Colombian friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you know where the\Nproper authorities are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady, does this look like the tourist\Nor employment agency to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really clumsy. She can't clean\Nor do chores, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta is much stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the damned things to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not gonna throw\Na teacup at me, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what you say is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd even believe it if you said Jesus\Ntore across Route 66 on a chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen her when she was strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't. But I remember one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived at my father's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us, my father,\NRoberta and I, lived peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have many friends to play with,\Nso Roberta would play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I especially loved\Nto arm wrestle with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I could beat Roberta every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta lost every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was arm wrestling me\Non that day, too, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To threaten my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew what was going on\Nlong before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment she sensed that they\Nwere coming, she stiffened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to beat her with\Nmy usual strength, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her arm was like steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta always lost to me on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized then, that she had a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to always act like a weak maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen nobility. The wife\Ndied four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones pictured are the head,\NDiego, his only son, Garcia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and their only servant, the house maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this. This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade Sergeant. Take a look\Nat her eyes. Don't you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes of a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all. She's one\Nhell of a rabid dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman. I've got business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a woman in a strange\Nmaid's outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is looking for the Colombian mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a crazy outfit that you'd only see\Nin Hollywood movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any idiot would remember someone\Nin clothes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called us here. What are you after?\NWho the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my intention to have you find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are from the\NManisarera cartel, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a servant of the Lovelace family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a few things I would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll excuse me, but I am afraid\NI may have to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?\N"Be rude", she says. This bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- She makes me laugh!\N- What are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid I will not be able to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a killer robot from the future!
